ary 2020}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/features/winners-of-nokia-16th-annual-star-screen-awards-2009/|title=Winners of Nokia 16th Annual Star Screen Awards 2009|website=Bollywood Hungama|date=9 January 2010|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| Imtiaz Ali\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Story|Best Story]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Screenplay|Best Screenplay]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Dialogue|Best Dialogue]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Saif Ali Khan\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| Deepika Padukone\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Supporting Actor|Best Supporting Actor]]\n| Rishi Kapoor\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Female Debut|Best Female Debut]]\n| [[Giselli Monteiro]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Music Director|Best Music Director]]\n| Pritam\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Male Playback|Best Male Playback Singer]]\n| [[Rahat Fateh Ali Khan]] (\"Aaj Din Chadheya\")\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Lyricist|Best Lyricist]]\n| Irshad Kamil (\"Chor Bazaari\")\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Award for Best Editing|Best Editing]]\n| [[Aarti Bajaj]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Sound Design\n| Dileep Subramanian\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\"| 17 January 2010\n| rowspan=\"7\"| [[Stardust Awards]]\n| [[Stardust Award for Best Film of the Year|Best Film of the Year]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''Love Aaj Kal''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"7\"| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainmenttags/max-stardust-awards/nominations-max-stardust-awards-2010|title=Nominations for Max Stardust Awards 2010|website=Pinkvilla|date=18 January 2010|access-date=14 February 2020}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/features/winners-of-max-stardust-awards-2010/|title=Winners of Max Stardust