{"title_page": "Ivchenko-Progress Motor Sich AI-450S", "text_new": "<!-- This article is a part of [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Aircraft]]. Please see [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Aircraft/page content]] for recommended layout. -->\n{|{{Infobox Aircraft Begin\n |name= AI-450S\n |image= \n |caption= \n}}\n{{Infobox Aircraft Engine\n |type= [[Turboprop]]\n |national origin = {{flagicon|Ukraine}}[[Ukraine]]\n |manufacturer= [[Ivchenko-Progress]]\n |first run= \n |major applications= [[Diamond DA50|D\u041050]]-JP7, [[Evektor EV-55|EV-55]], [[Diamond Dart 450|Dart 450]], [[Bayraktar Ak\u0131nc\u0131]]\n |number built =  \n |program cost = \n |unit cost = \n |developed from = \n |variants with their own articles =\n |developed into = \n}}\n|}\n\nThe '''AI-450S''' is a [[turboprop]] engine designed by [[Ivchenko-Progress]] and manufactured by [[Motor Sich]]. It is a two-shaft design with one gas generator shaft and one free turbine shaft. The 450 hp AI-450S is used on the [[Diamond DA50]]-JP7, [[Bayraktar Ak\u0131nc\u0131]] UAV and [[Diamond Dart 450]] and the 630 hp AI-450S-2 is used on the [[Evektor EV-55]].\n\n==Specification==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! model !! AI-450S<ref name=\"AI-450S\"/> !! AI-450S-2<ref name=\"AI-450S-2\"/>\n|-\n| Dimensions || 1,108 \u0445 575 \u0445 702 mm || 1,120 \u0445 578 \u0445 700 mm \n|-\n| Weight, dry || 130 kg || 140 kg\n|-\n| Take-off power || 450 hp || 630 hp\n|-\n| Take-off fuel consumption || 280 g/hp/h || 259 g/hp/h\n|-\n| Cruise power || 280 hp || 544 hp\n|-\n| Cruise fuel consumption || 280 g/hp/h || 246 g/hp/h\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Aircontent\n|related=\n|similar engines=\n* [[Pratt & Whitney Canada PT6]]\n* [[Rolls-Royce 250]]\n|lists=\n* [[List of aircraft engines]]\n|see also=\n}}\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"AI-450S\">{{cite web |url= http://ivchenko-progress.com/?portfolio=%D0%B0%D0%B8-450%D1%81&lang=en |title= AI-450S \u0422urboprop |publisher= [[Ivchenko-Progress]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AI-450S-2\">{{cite web |